name: COVID19SARSCoV2SARSCoVInfluenzaVirusAAndBTests
title: COVID 19 (SARS CoV 2), SARS CoV, Influenza virus A and B Tests
description: This value set may undergo changes until the HL7 Multiple Chronic Care FHIR IG is formally published in 2024.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains laboratory observable panel codes for COVID-19 (SARS-CoV-2), SARS-CoV, and Influenza virus A and B Tests.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients with a lab test performed on a source of blood, serum, or plasma for  COVID-19 (SARS-CoV-2), SARS-CoV, and Influenza virus A and B Tests.),(Inclusion Criteria: COVID-19 (SARS-CoV-2), SARS-CoV, and Influenza virus A and B lab tests using the source of blood, serum, or plasma, coded in LOINC, using panel codes and test codes (individual laboratory observations) associated with these panel code(s).),(Exclusion Criteria: Does not include any codes or concepts which do not represent COVID-19 (SARS-CoV-2), SARS-CoV, and Influenza virus A and B tests as defined in the inclusion criteria.)
